<DATE_TIME> 1998-10-12 01:37 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1274 &Cx1f; tic-z
r s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-FBC-ARIZONA-FOLLOW-AZ     10-12 0635
