</P>
<P>
   FILM-REVIEW-MIGHTY (San Francisco) _ There's a scene in ``The
Mighty'' when Sharon Stone is told her crippled son's health is
deteriorating. She walks over to a coffee machine in the hospital,
murmurs something about getting hot chocolate, then breaks down in
a rage against the machine as it slops liquid over a cup, slamming
and kicking it until tears spill from her eyes. By EDVINS BEITIKS.
</P>
<P>
   SPORTS (``s'' category)
</P>
<P>
   OUTDOORS-COLUMN (San Francisco) _ For $50, Tim Ford will tell
you all about the Bigfoot he saw last weekend. He'll explain how on
Saturday night, when he was roasting marshmallows at a campsite in
Northern California, he heard a loud rustling in some nearby
bushes, and that's when it all started. By TOM STIENSTRA.
</P>
