system. Their research led to a method of initiating penis erection
and indirectly to the development of the Viagra anti-impotency
drug. The three were Robert Furchgott, 82, of New York; Ferid
Murad, 62, of Houston, and Louis Ignarro, 57, of Los Angeles. By
