<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ELIMINATE-KOSOVO-MILOSEVIC-NYT </SLUG>
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORS:
</P>
<P>
   KOSOVO-MILOSEVIC (Belgrade) will not move in tonight's New York
Times News Service file.
</P>
<P>
   N.Y.Times News Service, Oct. 12.
</P>
