L.A. MALLS MAY GET AUSSIE ACCENT
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
BY ENRIQUE RIVERO  
 c.1998 Los Angeles Daily News  
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   &LR; LOS ANGELES _ The Topanga Plaza and Promenade mall could take
on Australian accents under a one-stop concept the shopping
